item.title: I got stunk
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Yes, to spawn an NPC, you would put it into the autospawn.cfg file. To change the starting equipment/armour, open up Item.java and search for:

playerEquipment[playerHat]

After this code, you will see a few numbers, this is the item ID that will be in the head spot (helmet/hat), below that, you will see some more of these, these are the other armour spots, to change the item’s you are given, just change the item ID.
